node.text:
Visit @SculptMovements 💕 for workouts, routine, and everythin else you eed to become fit! .
Treino de MMI com 01. Agachamento máquina 15/12/10 + drop com extensora 4 x 4 / 4x3 / 4x2 /4x 1 aumentando a carga ( 1 série ) 
1 x 10 com pico de contração em cima + 10 saindo da inércia 
1 x 10 com excêntrica lenta + 10 concêntrica lenta + 10 
02. Stiff 3 x 15 + bom dia 10 
03. Flexora 9 x 6 alternando a carga entre leva e pesado 
1 x 30 curtas + 10 isometria + 12 
1 x unilateral 8 /7/6 até zerar sem intervalo 
04. Flexora em pé 3 x 12 parando no meio + glúteo no cabo 3 x 12 
Panturrilhas sempre 😅
Macacão @santtaloren
.
.
.
Credit @graoficial #Fitness #fitfam #fitspo #motivation #workout #workoutvideo #legday #gym #abs

node.text:
❌Circuit instructions❌

Perform each exercise for ⏰40 seconds

rest ONLY 15 seconds before moving onto the next exercise 😴 Rest 1 min after the last exercise. 🌀3 rounds total .credit : @anita_herbert
.
.
.
#Fitness #fitfam #fitspo #motivation #workout #workoutvideo #legday #gym #abs

5 EXERCISES FOR THE ‘UNDER BUTT’ Follow us (@GymGlutes) for the best daily workout tips 💪

Who’s watched our latest YouTube with @hattieboydle ? 

We talk all things the ‘under but’ and give a very detailed walk through of each exercise and how to perform them! 

I’ve taken my favourite 5 and I’m going to hit your with a spicy workout🌶 

1. 8x Barbell Squat (High Bar) 
4 Sets 

1. 8x Barbell Romanian Deadlifts 
4 Sets 

1. 8x DB Split Squats (glute focused)
3 Sets 

1. 15x BB Good Mornings 
2. 20x DB Walking Lunges (glute Focused)
3 Sets 
Credit @racheljdillon

FULL BODY BURN 🔥 aka DE TODITO 💪🏼 Full body workout you can do at home or at the gym. Equipment needed: 1 dumbbell that’s it 👊🏼 TAG your babes and tell them to workout together! 
SAVE, SHARE AND LET’S CRUSH IT ❤️‍🔥

Method: total of 7 exercises - repeat each exercise 3 times - 45sec ON - 10sec OFF
-

Método: total de 7 ejercicios - repite cada ejercicio 3 veces - 45seg ON y 10seg OFF 

GUARDA ESTA RUTINA, COMPÁRTELA Y NOS FUIMOS ❤️‍🔥

node.text:
SAVE & SHARE for your next workout 💪
.
Do these exercises either as part of your warm up or on a recovery day between workouts. NOTE: the pistol squat is NOT considered part of this workout 😅.
.
Slow & steady. Focus on keeping your hips even and knees facing forward — no shifting or twisting. 👉 Once you can do 12-15 reps PER SIDE with good form, then you can increase range of motion and / or add weight.
.
The goal is not to “feel the burn” or be out of breath doing these. Quality over quantity, so we can keep those knees happy and healthy!
.
If you found this helpful, make sure to SAVE & SHARE for your next workout! 💛💪

credit @abby

Home Booty Growth! Click link in bio for bands 🍑 

Exercises: 
1️⃣ Hip thrust 
2️⃣ Seated abduction 
3️⃣ B-stance deadlift
4️⃣ Squat + 3 pulses 
5️⃣ Alternating kick back
6️⃣ Alternating double side kick
7️⃣ Seated abduction variation
Complete 3 - 4 rounds/sets, 10 - 30 reps or maximum reps depending on your level 🙌🏽
.
.
.
.
.
Credit @mariataftesund #Fitness #fitfam #fitspo #motivation #workout #workoutvideo #legday #gym #abs

node.text:
Lots of blood, sweat, and tears. 🤪

Credit @healthy.herbivore

Visit @SculptMobility for daily pain management, flexibility, and workout advice📚 

 Squat hack gym / home 🏋🏻‍♀️🏠⁣
⁣
The best way is to prioritize deep and complete movement so that you can reach the activation of all the muscles of the leg. ⁣
⁣
❤️ IMPORTANT TIP: Here it also plays an important role in the leg position, I did it in both videos with the legs at shoulder height, here we involve quadriceps, hamstrings and glutes. This position is the one that you should not stop doing before changing to another, it is to achieve that your legs are built with equal proportion.
.
EXECUTION TYP: place the ball on the buttocks, you can also use a soccer ball that are harder, I used a plastic ball for a child. ⁣
⁣
Write down the ideas of other devices you need to record me when I can go to the gym ❤️
.
.
.
credit: @aleestefania #abworkout #coreworkout #quadsworkout #legworkout #gluteworkout #workoutvideos  #gymmotivation #bodybuilding #fitnessmotivation #homeworkout #fullbodyworkout #bodyweightworkout
